S=\frac{n(n+1)}{2}
\sum_{k=1}^n\frac{1}{(2k-1)(2k+1)}=\sum_{k=1}^n\frac12\left(\frac{1}{2k-1}-\frac{1}{2k+1}\right)=\frac12\left(1-\frac{1}{2n+1}\right)=\frac n{2n+1}
